data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom 2.1 bath.  Absolutely perfect, spacious, & seriously upgraded 2013 rehab.  New roof, gutters, plumbing, electric, walls, floors, etc.  All 3 levels are cable ready.  Carpet, cabinets, lighting, & tile upgrades throughout.  Exhaust fans in bathrooms.  Heating ducks in floors rather than ceilings.  Large bedrooms.  Lots of storage.  Totally finished basement.  Very big yard with custom landscaping and enough room for you to do some planing.  Two car garage with electric door openers, power, and lighting.  Like I said, absolutely perfect.
data.whatILove: This gut rehab was done with the end-user in mind.  The cable for TV and internet services has been put in every room including the basement family room.  The finishes in the basement are as quality as the main and upper floors.  The doors all have door stops.  The master bedroom walk-in closet has been arranged for maximum benefit, including shoe storage shelving.  The lighting is upgraded throughout, recessed in the main areas including the basement.  The breakfast island cabinet in the kitchen has electricity and the cabinet in the bathroom has a slide out shelf.  The paint job is custom and beautiful.  The central air and heat vents are in the floors not the ceilings which maximizes the functioning.  I don't think they spared any comfort.
